   <refbody>
      <table colsep="1" rowsep="1" class="- topic/table ">
         <desc class="- topic/desc ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">The following table provides the workflow actions and status (current and subsequent status) of the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Program</uicontrol> record.</p>
            <p product="Exclude_PG_Content" class="- topic/p ">For information on setting a workflow status to the next status, refer to <xref href="../../Common_Application_Features/Workflow_Management/WFStgTrans.dita"
                     class="- topic/xref ">Workflow Status Transitions</xref>.</p>
         </desc>
         <tgroup cols="6" class="- topic/tgroup ">
            <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <colspec colname="c3" colnum="3" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <colspec colname="c4" colnum="4" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <colspec colname="c5" colnum="5" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <colspec colname="c6" colnum="6" class="- topic/colspec "/>
            <thead class="- topic/thead ">
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Phase</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Current Workflow Status</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Stakeholders</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Action</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Subsequent Workflow Status</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Comments</entry>
               </row>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">1</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Draft</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <ul class="- topic/ul ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">Fund Manager</li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">Program Manager</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Submit</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Submitted</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">-</entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">2</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">Submitted</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">Fund Manager</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Approve</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Approved</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">On approval of a program, the following changes occur:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">The published budget estimates of the projects that are part of the program are approved. Also, thecurrent budget of each project is updated with the approved budget estimate items. </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">If what-if analysisis done, then the project start and end dates, forecast dates, and current budget datesare updated based on the forecast changes done in the program.  </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li "> The workflow status of each project that is part of the program is set to<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Planned</uicontrol>if the start date of the project is not in the current yearand is set to <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Pre-Award</uicontrol>if the start date of the project is in the current year. </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">A project is moved from the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Planned Projects </uicontrol>list to the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Projects </uicontrol>module list page if the workflow status of the project is set to <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Pre-Award</uicontrol>. The project remains in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Planned Projects </uicontrol>list page if the workflow status of the project is set to <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Planned</uicontrol>. </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">Forecast snapshot is   generated automatically when the program is approved.</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Redraft</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Draft</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">-</entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">3</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">Approved</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">Fund Manager</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Close</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">Closed</entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">-</entry>
